                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=wadearnold",
                        "name": "wadearnold",
                        "displayName": "Wade Arnold",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I really like this idea and something similar was part of the initial proposal. The issue that we had was that we really wanted to be able to cache the lookup the reflected lookup table for subsequent requests. We were worried about performance but is something that I hope we can add after the 1.8 release. ",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=wadearnold",
                        "name": "wadearnold",
